'''Vongspawn''' was a derogatory term for [[Sentience/Legends|sentients]] infected with [[Vongspawn virus]] as a result of the sabotaged [[Ossus Project]]. Many had looked to the [[Fel Empire|Galactic Empire]] for aid, not aware that the Empire was in league with the Project's original saboteurs, the [[One Sith|Sith Order]]. A large population of Vongspawn lived in [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant's]] [[Coruscant Underworld/Legends|underlevels]].

